Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦突入 便没有退路了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以确定的只有…现在非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解是也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.43,0:01:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候就会得出答案了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为一个火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（突入）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜…保护了我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是个密斯提司的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要把悠二给…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,8)}{\bord2\1c&H3535FF&\3c&HCFCFCF&}星黎殿的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子没有布下结界是也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 应该非常清楚我们已经突入了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（不可大意）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在星黎殿里应该住着「扮装舞会」的红世之徒们的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太安静了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连磷子的气息都没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在这里面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断溢出庞大的存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎并不打算把零时迷子藏起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（陷阱）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 已经没有时间来慎重地应付了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你就叫夏娜好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们其中一人先到达零时迷子那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就还有宛转余地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用理会对方 只管前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的…你的答案是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（时间紧迫）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手竟然是那么大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都布满了像自在式一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨碍实验的鼠辈们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多~~米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是~~准备完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨碍实验的人就用来实验
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来我「浑之圣庙」这个题目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就拿她们来进行回收再利用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红世之徒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙…是磷子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（机器人偶）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「探耽求究」么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿~~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在之力给吸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大成功~！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把入侵者的力量吸收进温酒瓶内加以利用的自在法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs26}译者按：温酒瓶应该是指储存「存在之力」的容器　　神经病教授对它的爱称
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是优秀的作品~~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 教授
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「探耽求究」那混蛋 耍这种卑鄙的伎俩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是让我们轻松进来的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这些磷子却在动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是那家伙做了特别处理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贽殿遮那…好重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 所能依靠的只有自身掌握的体术了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起在天道宫时的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:09:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有朝着零时迷子前进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面明明充斥着存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜她…正在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市里充满了存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为零时迷子的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实想要保护城市的话这样是最好的也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是个单纯的密斯提司
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要进入我里面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:11:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你正在进入我的里面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的思念正在填满着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今为止一直在祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻求着答案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这肯定就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…再给我…再把你给我些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  到底能撑到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要赌一下 「千变」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手可是那个「天壤之劫火」和「梦幻之冠带」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为容器的火焰之雾如果不能使用存在之力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就和普通的人类一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且「浑之圣庙」已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在之力只会永远地增加下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在那里战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊 平井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 存在之力开始活性化了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没完没了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是在计算之中么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为礼炮来说似乎有点夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精~~~彩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才正是谁也没见过的 注入过盛存在之力的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教…教授 以后会变什么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为不知道才要做实验
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了了解这世界的一切 法则 真理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学 小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙…虽然不知道发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总觉得大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  这城市到底会变成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启作 荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:15:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说听没听到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启作 荣太  快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈 看来还活着呢 两位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为那个什么火焰之雾的使命的玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真敢说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是拼命赶过来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管了 马上去玻璃檀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事要调查
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…所以说那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说早就在玻璃檀等着啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要调查什么快给我说出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈 干得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 刚才的口气就当我没听到好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看下星黎殿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星黎殿？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是浮在空中大得要死的城堡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼们好像冲进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却中了奇怪的自在法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查一下这个自在式是从城堡的哪里发出的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教育的成果呢 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是不错的小弟们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐藤 回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐她回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是任性的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一首动听的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 再来一首动听的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了 好好听着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 再来一首动听的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正中靶心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:17:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎…迎击用的自在法发生装置给…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你~~说~~~什~~~么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「悼词咏唱者」像是回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 为什么火焰之雾要到处破坏新的尝试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把她们一起吸进去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫卡特也会分心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话我也不得不动手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来被「悼词咏唱者」救了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个气息是…「悖论裁决者」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎大驾光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是应该说声「好久不见了」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是希望你不要碍事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都做了那么奇怪的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可不允许中途退出哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围也充满了存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此尽全力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在变成冤家之前分个高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一个人到就行了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案…应该已经有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于密斯提司的破坏…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会破坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思说要让世界的平衡崩溃么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不会让它发生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比鲁海尔米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是炎发灼眼的讨伐者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还有另一个叫夏娜的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命会完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却不想把密斯提司…悠二破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一个都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少了哪个都不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是单纯的火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为炎发灼眼的夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只进行自己所相信的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走是也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你已经决定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说下去也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比鲁海尔米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我坚信着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信那是纯粹的你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗之后再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「万能的巧匠」「梦幻之冠带」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 突然就逃了可真不尽人情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的对手乃我是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（开战）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦~~稍微让我乐一乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿拉斯拖鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问过我想把悠二怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让他怎么样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还没有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…喜欢悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只想到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…只有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这个就能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你就叫夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从现在开始就这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不是单纯的火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎发灼眼的火焰之雾？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我起的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:22:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时起 炎发灼眼的火焰之雾就变成了夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 因为是夏娜才会救我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是夏娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.03,0:22:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 因为不是普通的火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.55,0:22:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样…我不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她看成普通的火焰之雾的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是我自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.41,0:22:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨碍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二…绝对要救你！
